    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建您自己的水族馆并收集鱼类。在舒适的环境中游泳，鱼儿会给您带来平和与幸福。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以做其他任务或任何您想做的事。随着时间的推移，鱼儿会开始填满大海。您无法阻止流动的波浪。鱼儿可能会离开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您发现了新品种的鱼吗？有特别颜色的鱼吗？有您想放入水族馆的鱼吗？如果有，就抓住它。鱼儿们会很乐意进入您的水族馆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197730/extras/b34ff306a122289b06eedb8121f72dd3.poster.avif?t=1729706166\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197730/extras/b34ff306a122289b06eedb8121f72dd3.webm?t=1729706166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197730/extras/b34ff306a122289b06eedb8121f72dd3.mp4?t=1729706166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放松。听音乐，清空您的思绪。 享受观赏您的鱼儿！</p>",
